message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to present our premium product to you. It's a unique opportunity that aligns perfectly with your needs and interests. Given its exceptional value, we believe it's worth $12000 to you. To make this deal attractive for both parties, I propose a price of $11000. This allows us to cover our costs while ensuring you get a great deal on an item that's truly worth more to you. Please let me know if you're interested in proceeding with this offer.
